Reasoning: 
1. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper focuses on the optimization of network energy efficiency in a cloud radio access network, which falls under the scope of networking and internet architecture.
2. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper involves the formulation of an optimization problem with constraints, which can be related to information theory.
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with the control data separation architecture and resource allocation, which can be considered as a system and control problem.
4. cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) - The paper involves the optimization of resource allocation in a cloud radio access network, which can be related to distributed and parallel computing.
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper mentions over-the-top (OTT) content service, which can be related to multimedia applications.
